    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, that fellow, he was a rank of-- of-- of-- of [GERMAN] was his title.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told me [SPEAKING GERMAN], which means, I would whistle on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, from now on, nobody's going to bother you anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, you can work over here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody's going to bother you or force you to become a German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was-- out of the thousands of Germans that I knew, there were a few of them that had a little bit humanity in them.",
